=== Adjective ===
'''flag'''
# Of or pertaining to an [[admiral]], [[commodore]], or [[general]] officer
#:''Captains park in the second row, flag officers next to the building.''

=== Transitive verb ===
'''to flag'''  ([[flags]], [[flagged]], [[flagging]])
# {{cattag|Computing}}: to signal (an event).
#: ''The compiler flagged three errors.''
# {{cattag|Computing}}: to set a program variable to ''true''.
#: ''Flag the debug option before running the program.''
# (often with ''down'') to signal (someone) to stop.
#: ''Please flag a taxi down for me.''
# to lay down flagstones
#: ''Fred is planning to flag his patio this weekend.''

